- **來源**：[TechCrunch](https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/19/google-introduces-gemini-spark-a-24-7-agentic-assistant-with-gmail-integration/) · [CBS News](https://www.cbsnews.com/news/google-gemini-spark-ai-agent/) · 3 家媒體報導
